reviewText: Would not play on u.s.a. DVD player. Did ret urn and got speedy refund
Watching it now! Gotta have a Multi Region DVD player or be able to change the settings... happy I got this
Season 4 is the only season in this collection that is uncensored!  Season 1 isn't region free as stated in description. Mob Wives just isn't Mob Wives with beeps drowning out the cuss words...
